OL,5, Bankers can earn unlimited bonuses     
OL,6, again from Tuesday, following a change 
OL,7, to rules brought in following the      
OL,8, financial crisis.                      
OL,10,FBefore 2008 City high-flyers hit the   
OL,11,Fheadlines for spending their bonuses on
OL,12,Ffast cars and champagne-fuelled nights.
OL,14,FThe TUC warns removing the cap will    
OL,15,Fbring back a "greed is good" culture.  
OL,17,FBut UK Finance, the body representing  
OL,18,Fthe sector, says scrapping the cap will
OL,19,Fmake it easier to attract the best     
OL,20,Fprofessionals from around the world.   
